- cs.PL (Programming Languages) is another likely category as the paper deals with the syntax and semantics of programming languages. 
- cs.TL (Type Theory) is a possible category as the paper deals with simply-typed languages and their syntax. 
- cs.SE (Software Engineering) is a possible category as the paper deals with techniques for specifying and translating between programming languages. 
- cs.FL (Formal Languages and Automata Theory) is a possible category as the paper deals with the formal characterization of programming languages.
